  m_text: "Any of the following signs indicate that the individual is a Suret and
    must be REJECTED IMMEDIATELY.\n\n\u2022Possessing a non-human age.\n\u2022Red
    or white eye coloration is observed.\n\u2022Green discoloration of the skin.\n\u2022Body
    temperature below 36.0\xB0C or above 37.5\xB0C.\n\u2022Light produces an abnormal
    shadow.\n\u2022No image is visible inside the capsule."
